Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:57.41,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur10}向前划行  向前划行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur10}要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.95,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\1a&HFF&\blur10}无论去哪里
